        "subject": "LU-19842 tests: fix awk quoting in wait_all_targets_blocked()",
        "message": "LU-19842 tests: fix awk quoting in wait_all_targets_blocked()\n\nIn wait_all_targets_blocked(), the error handler uses awk with\nsingle quotes to extract the MDT count from lfsck_query output.\nSingle quotes prevent shell variable expansion of ${com} and\n${status}, so the awk pattern never matches and the error\nmessage shows an empty count: \"only of 4 MDTs are in completed\".\n\nFixes: 955e38051765 (\"LU-17385 tests: always_except sanity-lfsck/24\")\nSigned-off-by: Sohei Koyama <skoyama@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: I51baeab1d7421ceaa4f46a9338fce2ae3e33289d\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/64323\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@thelustrecollective.com>\nReviewed-by: Jian Yu <yujian@whamcloud.com>\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\n"
